---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import portrait from '../assets/raha-portrait.jpg';
import { site } from '../data/site';
---

<section id="about" class="section about">
  <div class="wrap about-grid">
    <div class="about-portrait" data-reveal>
      <Image
        src={portrait}
        alt="Raha Teimuri, Social Media Lead"
        widths={[360, 520, 720]}
        sizes="(max-width: 760px) 80vw, 380px"
        loading="lazy"
        class="portrait-img"
      />
      <span class="portrait-tag">Raha Teimuri</span>
    </div>

    <div class="about-copy" data-reveal>
      <span class="label" style="color:var(--accent)">// About</span>
      <h2 class="section-title-alt about-h">
        I grow brands to millions of followers without spending
        <span class="hl">a cent on ads</span>.
      </h2>
      <p class="about-p">
        I'm Raha, a Social Media Lead with 5+ years growing audiences online. I turn content into
        reach, reach into audience, and audience into revenue. I took a travel brand from zero to
        over 1M organic followers, mostly American, directed videos to 50M+ views, and drove €80K a
        year in tracked bookings. I've done it across industries, from travel to music tech, and now
        I lead social for Yousician and GuitarTuna.
      </p>
      <p class="about-p">
        I know what makes people stop, share, and act, and I build the teams and systems to do it on
        repeat. AI is built into how I work: I direct production with tools like Superscale, and I
        use Claude to build systems, run research, and sharpen every hook, caption and brief. Going
        viral isn't luck for me. It's how I work.
      </p>
      <a href={site.cv} download class="btn btn-ink about-cv">Download CV</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 380px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .about-portrait { position: relative; }
  .portrait-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border: var(--bw) solid var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--r-card);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    display: block;
  }
  .portrait-tag {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 14px;
    left: -10px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    background: var(--lime);
    border: var(--bw) solid var(--ink);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
    padding: 8px 14px;
    border-radius: var(--r-pill);
    transform: rotate(-3deg);
  }
  .about-h { margin: 12px 0 18px; line-height: 1.08; }
  .about-p { font-size: var(--t-body-lg); line-height: 1.65; margin: 0 0 16px; max-width: 60ch; }
  .about-cv { margin-top: 10px; }

  @media (max-width: 760px) {
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 34px; }
    .about-portrait { max-width: 340px; }
  }
</style>
